      <description>&lt;p&gt;I needed a base image &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.vagrantup.com/v2/boxes.html&#34;&gt;box&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo; for my &lt;a title=&#34;Automatically deploying GlusterFS with Puppet-Gluster + Vagrant!&#34; href=&#34;https://purpleidea.com/blog/automatically-deploying-glusterfs-with-puppet-gluster-vagrant/&#34;&gt;Puppet-Gluster+Vagrant&lt;/a&gt; work. It would have been great if good boxes already existed, and even better if it were easy to build my own. As it turns out, I wasn&amp;rsquo;t able to satisfy either of these conditions, so I&amp;rsquo;ve had to build one myself! &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/purpleidea/puppet-gluster/blob/master/builder/README&#34;&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve published all of my code&lt;/a&gt;, so that you can use these techniques and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/purpleidea/puppet-gluster/blob/master/builder/Makefile&#34;&gt;tools&lt;/a&gt; too!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
